modName: More lore-friendly-- Julianos shrine - Wolfskull cave
summary: Removes the real-world freemason & eye of providence symbols from their textures
descriptionHtml:
I don't know why those symbols were placed within their respective textures, but they're not for Skyrim, and are bad for immersion.

I've included optional: 'accented' or 'tarnished silver' skins for the Shrine of Julianos as well.
Uses "High Resolution Texture Pack" textures

Manual install only
